document_data.name: Highport
document_data.mainbody: '''Highport''' was an island within the [[Korinn Archipelago]] in the [[Moonshae Isles]].{{Cite interactive atlas}}{{Cite dungeon/196/Backdrop: Moonshae Isles|11}}
document_data.Geography: Highport was located just northeast of the island of [[Caftenor]]. Highport was also less than {{SI|10|mi|k|long=yes}} off the coast of the far northern tip of [[Gnarhelm]] on [[Alaron]]. A large unnamed mountain peak dominated much of the southern half of the island. A small forest was found in the northern half.
